# 🧠 Memory Training Game

## What is this app?
This memory game is designed to help you exercise your brain and improve memory. It's easy to play with large, colorful cards and a fun, interactive layout!

## Features:
- 🧩 Simple matching game to test your memory.
- 💡 Fun card flipping animations for a playful experience.
- 🕹️ Easy-to-use with clear visual design and large cards.
- 🎨 Beautiful background and colors that make the game more engaging.

## How to use:
1. Click on two cards to flip them over and see if they match.
2. Keep flipping cards until you match all pairs.
3. When all cards are matched, celebrate! 🎉

## Designed for:
- All ages, especially elderly users who want to improve their memory.
- Fun, colorful, and easy-to-navigate game interface.
